    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is priced accordingly \u2014 best suited for mechanically inclined buyers, those seeking a project car, or anyone in need of a parts vehicle. The exterior shows significant wear, including visible rust, dents, and faded or damaged paint in multiple areas. The interior is worn and shows considerable age, with torn upholstery, cracked trim, and non-functional components. Mechanically, the vehicle has known issues and will require repairs before it can be considered reliably roadworthy. We strongly recommend a thorough inspection prior to purchase. No warranties are implied or offered. What you see is what you get \u2014 this is an as-is sale for a buyer who knows what they're taking on.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
